Core Value Proposition
Position around saving time, reducing admin, and helping tradespeople focus on the work that earns them money — not paperwork.

1. “Stop losing jobs to missed calls and double bookings”
Tradespeople lose revenue through scheduling chaos. Emphasize how the platform eliminates conflicts, captures every job request, and keeps the calendar airtight.
2. “Get paid faster with less chasing”
Link scheduling to invoicing — when jobs are booked and completed in one system, billing happens automatically. Cash flow is a top pain point for small trades businesses.
3. “Your customers expect a professional experience”
Online booking, automated reminders, and job confirmations signal legitimacy. Help trades businesses look as professional as larger competitors.
4. “Built for the tools-in-hand reality”
Mobile-first, fast, and simple. Tradespeople aren’t at a desk — the platform has to work on a phone in a van or on a job site with one hand free.
5. “Dispatch your team without the phone tag”
For businesses with multiple technicians, the value is real-time visibility — who’s where, what’s next, and who’s available. Reduce management overhead dramatically.
6. “Never lose a repeat customer again”
Automated follow-ups, service history, and reminders for recurring jobs (annual boiler service, HVAC maintenance, etc.) turn one-off clients into loyal customers.
7. “Set it up in an afternoon, see results this week”
Reduce friction to adoption. Trades buyers are skeptical of complexity — a fast time-to-value message overcomes hesitation.

Audience-Specific Angles
	•	Solo traders: “Run your whole business from your phone”
	•	Small teams (2–10): “Coordinate your crew without constant calls”
	•	Larger contractors: “Reduce dispatcher workload and increase job throughput”

Proof Points to Build In
	•	Average time saved per week
	•	% reduction in no-shows (via reminders)
	•	Revenue recovered from previously missed bookings
	•	Customer rating improvements
The strongest overall message tends to be: more jobs completed, less time on admin, happier customers — all from one simple tool.
